        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-7367a812-7904-443e-af35-bb783ceca300">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-7367a812-7904-443e-af35-bb783ceca300">
                Mr. Muff  (Hull, East)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-7367a812-7904-443e-af35-bb783ceca300" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1942-10-13/debates/61a48ab7-82f9-479b-a7d2-1a847f4cff8a/Clause1%E2%80%94(ContinuanceOf2And3Geo6C115)#contribution-7367a812-7904-443e-af35-bb783ceca300">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">On a point of Order. What Amendment is the hon. Member moving?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-7367a812-7904-443e-af35-bb783ceca300" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1942-10-13/debates/61a48ab7-82f9-479b-a7d2-1a847f4cff8a/Clause1%E2%80%94(ContinuanceOf2And3Geo6C115)#contribution-7367a812-7904-443e-af35-bb783ceca300">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-12ac3642-e1a1-4547-92ec-f11c1bedf983">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-12ac3642-e1a1-4547-92ec-f11c1bedf983">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-12ac3642-e1a1-4547-92ec-f11c1bedf983">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-12ac3642-e1a1-4547-92ec-f11c1bedf983">
                Mr. Lipson
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-12ac3642-e1a1-4547-92ec-f11c1bedf983" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1942-10-13/debates/61a48ab7-82f9-479b-a7d2-1a847f4cff8a/Clause1%E2%80%94(ContinuanceOf2And3Geo6C115)#contribution-12ac3642-e1a1-4547-92ec-f11c1bedf983">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">The first Amendment. During the war we have surrendered a great many of our liberties in order that a greater liberty may be preserved, but it is the duty of Parliament to see that these berties are not unnecessarily suspended, <span id="1562" class="column-number" data-column-number="1562"></span> and I want to suggest that by accepting the suggestion to extend the period of this Bill to March instead of December and so enabling the Government to take appropriate measures to bring in another Bill——</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-12ac3642-e1a1-4547-92ec-f11c1bedf983" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1942-10-13/debates/61a48ab7-82f9-479b-a7d2-1a847f4cff8a/Clause1%E2%80%94(ContinuanceOf2And3Geo6C115)#contribution-12ac3642-e1a1-4547-92ec-f11c1bedf983">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-28812762-07f0-4a6a-be9e-f219e8fbfafa">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-28812762-07f0-4a6a-be9e-f219e8fbfafa">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-28812762-07f0-4a6a-be9e-f219e8fbfafa">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-28812762-07f0-4a6a-be9e-f219e8fbfafa">
                The Deputy-Chairman
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-28812762-07f0-4a6a-be9e-f219e8fbfafa" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1942-10-13/debates/61a48ab7-82f9-479b-a7d2-1a847f4cff8a/Clause1%E2%80%94(ContinuanceOf2And3Geo6C115)#contribution-28812762-07f0-4a6a-be9e-f219e8fbfafa">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">I think any discussion on temporary vacancies must be out of Order. We cannot discuss that on this Amendment or on the later Amendment, because, as the hon. Member no doubt understands, one cannot amend a Bill which is purely a continuation Bill I do not think one can allow any discussion on the question of casual vacancies.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-28812762-07f0-4a6a-be9e-f219e8fbfafa" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1942-10-13/debates/61a48ab7-82f9-479b-a7d2-1a847f4cff8a/Clause1%E2%80%94(ContinuanceOf2And3Geo6C115)#contribution-28812762-07f0-4a6a-be9e-f219e8fbfafa">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





